column5: Sleep in late?...Nope !...Take it easy after a long and busy day today serving up burgers, sausages, hot dogs and chicken with Loonietoon and Little Cliff?...Nope!...  You guessed it...go icefishing up at Uncle Jack's pond...  If you are in the neighborhood, drop by and say hello...
Have fun Lads... and play safe ! I'll be cleaning the house up!
Have fun gents, I'll be asleep  Maureen
